<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Coffee Shop</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Bootstrap Icons -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('nav.ejs'); %>
    <div id="coffeeCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-indicators">
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#coffeeCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="0" class="active" aria-current="true" aria-label="Slide 1"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#coffeeCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="1" aria-label="Slide 2"></button>
            <button type="button" data-bs-target="#coffeeCarousel" data-bs-slide-to="2" aria-label="Slide 3"></button>
        </div>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="carousel-item active">
                <img src="images/citem1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="images/citem2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="images/citem3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            </div>
            <div class="carousel-item">
                <img src="images/citem4.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="...">
            </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#coffeeCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#coffeeCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
        </button>
    </div>

    <section id="top-picks">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center my-4">Top Picks</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Add your product items here -->
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/top1.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Product 1">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">LavAzza Gran Espresso Beans</h5>
                            <a href="product_link1.html" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/top2.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Product 1">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Breville Barista Express Espresso Machine</h5>
                            <a href="product_link1.html" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4 mb-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img src="images/top3.jpg" class="card-img-top" alt="Product 1">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">Bodum Double Wall Pour Over Coffee Maker</h5>
                            <a href="product_link1.html" class="btn btn-primary">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
            </div>
            <!-- "View All" button -->
            <div class="text-center mt-4">
                <a href="/viewall" class="btn btn-primary">View All</>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section id="about-us" class="py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="text-center mb-4">About Us</h2>
            <p class="col-lg-6">
                Welcome to [name], the ultimate haven for coffee enthusiasts and connoisseurs alike. Born from a passion for the rich tapestry of coffee culture, our platform is more than just a marketplace; it's a journey into the heart of coffee craftsmanship. 
    
                At [name], we believe that every sip of coffee tells a story – from the sun-drenched hills where the beans are harvested, to the skilled hands that craft the machines and grinders. That's why we’ve curated an expansive collection of coffee-related products, including artisanal beans, state-of-the-art espresso machines, and precision grinders, ensuring that you can bring the essence of the world's best coffee houses right into your home.
    
                Our story began in a small college dorm, fueled by late-night study sessions and a shared love for coffee. We realized that each cup of coffee was an experience waiting to be savored and that access to the right tools and ingredients was key to unlocking this magic. Thus, BrewVerse was born – a platform that not only sells coffee and equipment but also celebrates the culture and artistry behind every cup.
    
                We partner with the finest coffee growers, roasters, and equipment manufacturers, focusing on sustainability, quality, and innovation. From exotic beans to the latest brewing technology, we bring it all to your fingertips.
    
                Dive into BrewVerse, where every grind, brew, and sip is an adventure. Let's embark on this caffeinated journey together, exploring the depths of flavor, aroma, and the sheer joy that coffee brings to our lives.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
    

    <footer class="bg-brown text-white text-center py-3">
        <p>&copy; 2023 [name]. All Rights Reserved.</p>
        <div class="social-icons">
            <a href="your_facebook_link" class="bi bi-facebook"></a>
            <a href="your_twitter_link" class="bi bi-twitter"></a>
            <a href="your_instagram_link" class="bi bi-instagram"></a>
            <!-- Add other social media links as needed -->
        </div>
    </footer>
    
    

    <!-- Bootstrap Bundle with Popper -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
